
BOOK MY SHOW - LLD Requirements:
==================================

Actors: [User, Theatre, System]
-------
User:
	--> Search for movies/theatres based on location/language
	--> Select the movie/theatre
	--> Select timing and seats
	--> Book Ticket
	--> Complete payment (add on apply promo/offer if there are any)
	--> Receive Booking Confirmation status - Email/SMS/Whatsapp

Theatre:
	--> Add/Modify/Remove Movies and Timings
	--> To block the seats during payment processing
	--> Send confirmation once payment completed.
		
System:
	--> Onboarding of theatres
	--> Review/Rating System
	--> Notification to theatres to block the seats during payment processing.
	--> Notification to users about booking status (processing/confirmed)
	--> Keep updating the current seat availability.
